sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuthSrv as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Backend Container<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prom as Prometheus Service<br/>9091/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Prom: Flow 1: User Authentication and Dashboard Access

    User->>Route: GET / (HTTPS)
    Route->>OAuth: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
    OAuth->>OAuthSrv: Validate Session / Authenticate<br/>Client Secret Auth
    OAuthSrv-->>OAuth: OAuth Token / Cookie
    OAuth->>Backend: GET / (HTTP)<br/>Bearer Token Injected
    Backend-->>OAuth: Frontend Static Assets (React App)
    OAuth-->>Route: HTTPS Response
    Route-->>User: Dashboard UI (Session Cookie)

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Kubernetes API Operations (e.g., Create Notebook)

    User->>Route: POST /api/notebooks<br/>HTTPS, Session Cookie
    Route->>OAuth: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
    OAuth->>Backend: POST /api/notebooks<br/>HTTP, Bearer Token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>HTTPS, Service Account Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: CR Created (200 OK)
    Backend-->>OAuth: Success Response (JSON)
    OAuth-->>Route: HTTPS Response
    Route-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User,Prom: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Query

    User->>Route: POST /api/prometheus/*<br/>HTTPS, Session Cookie
    Route->>OAuth: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
    OAuth->>Backend: POST /api/prometheus/*<br/>HTTP, Bearer Token
    Backend->>Prom: Prometheus Query (PromQL)<br/>HTTP, Bearer Token (user)
    Prom-->>Backend: Metrics Data (JSON)
    Backend-->>OAuth: Metrics Response
    OAuth-->>Route: HTTPS Response
    Route-->>User: Metrics Data

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 4: WebSocket Kubernetes Watch (e.g., Notebook Events)

    User->>Route: WebSocket /wss/k8s/*<br/>HTTPS Upgrade
    Route->>OAuth: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
    OAuth->>Backend: WebSocket /wss/k8s/*<br/>HTTP, Bearer Token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Watch Notebook CR<br/>WebSocket/HTTPS, Service Account Token

    loop Real-time Updates
        K8sAPI-->>Backend: Event Stream (WebSocket)
        Backend-->>OAuth: Event Stream (WebSocket)
        OAuth-->>Route: Event Stream (HTTPS)
        Route-->>User: Real-time Updates
    end
